<i>noun</i>: 하례 [하ː례], 경축 [경ː축] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>하례 [하ː례]</dt><br>
<dd>greeting; congratulation</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 축하하여 정식으로 인사를 드림.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of extending an official greeting in celebration of an event.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>경축 [경ː축]</dt><br>
<dd>celebration; congratulation</dd><br>
<dd>기쁘고 즐거운 일을 축하함.</dd><br>
<dd>Celebrating a happy and joyful occasion.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>